---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Evan at Evan Today for questions, feedback, or business inquiries.">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Contact</h1>
		<div class="prose">
			<p>
				Got a question about an article? Found something wrong? Want to suggest a topic?
				I read every email and try to reply within a day or two.
			</p>

			<h2>Email</h2>
			<p>
				<a href="mailto:hello@evantoday.id">hello@evantoday.id</a> — the best way to reach me for anything.
			</p>

			<h2>Business and advertising</h2>
			<p>
				If you're interested in advertising, sponsored content, or partnerships, email me
				with "Business" in the subject line. I only work with brands and products I'd
				genuinely recommend to my readers.
			</p>

			<h2>Corrections</h2>
			<p>
				I take accuracy seriously. If you spot an error in any article — wrong numbers,
				outdated info, broken links — please let me know and I'll fix it right away.
			</p>

			<h2>Where I'm based</h2>
			<p>
				I'm based in Indonesia. This blog covers personal finance topics primarily for
				an Indonesian and Southeast Asian audience.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
